{"tid":1480811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱烈狂賀颱風利奇馬殺死56隻蝗蟲","createTime":"2019-08-17T12:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T17:17:20.000Z","uid":38255,"like":80,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"25c8001edc3b7052d22562a54f4d72c944cf62b1","tid":1480811,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"利奇馬在8月10日凌晨以超強颱風下限登陸浙江省溫嶺市，為當地帶來嚴重破壞。隨後利奇馬北上橫掃華東沿岸並減弱。截至2019年8月14日，浙江、上海、江蘇、山東、安徽、福建、河南、河北、天津、遼寧、吉林總受災人數為1,402.4萬人，緊急移轉安置204萬人，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">56人死亡、14人失蹤</span></strong>，房屋倒塌1.5萬餘間，11.9萬間不同程度毀壞，農作物受災面積996千公頃，直接經濟損失537.2億人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n因超強颱風利奇馬，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">累積停電戶數為759.17萬戶</span></strong>，其中浙江電力427.03萬戶、山東電力216.56萬戶、江蘇電力41.28萬戶、安徽電力33.2萬戶、河北電力24.91萬戶、福建電力8.63萬戶、上海電力5.58萬戶、遼寧電力9431戶、冀北電力4677戶、天津電力5600戶。<br />\n<br />\n人數過左35，非常大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本post係歡迎今日帝吧出精既同志，分享下自己係咪停電果七百幾萬戶啱啱先有返電？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9bac882810487ae18063e2d936c68813661ec5","tid":1480811,"uid":59225,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:46:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">８１８安排</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 慢慢排入維園，入唔到就<span style=\"color: gold;\">坐低</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">直至集會結束為止</span><br />\n2. 集會結束後，不建議由天后或銅鑼灣走，<span style=\"color: red;\">去金鐘或中環走</span></span>"},{"pid":"b07dc3d3e3861f1eb8037766dfa01153e9abcc0d","tid":1480811,"uid":69037,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"重建又可以谷gdp<br />\nGogogo"},{"pid":"aabe11324f0dacbfcedfebc7974aafa365667625","tid":1480811